{"tid":1644730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警方MON中大對話會女學生指控警方新屋嶺扣留中心被警員性侵。","createTime":"2019-10-10T16:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:53:15.000Z","uid":244704,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"609dd58c74422a7facd7a1ca844171266a44500a","tid":1644730,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"警方留意到今日（十月十日）晚上，在一個大學對話會中，一名女學生指稱被警方拘捕後，曾在新屋嶺扣留中心被警員性侵。<br />\n<br />\n警方非常重視上述嚴重指控。直至目前為止，投訴警察課並沒有接獲在新屋嶺扣留中心被性侵的投訴。警方將會主動聯絡事主，希望她提供實質證據，讓警方作出公平公正的調查，盡快找出事實真相。<br />\n<br />\nThe Police are aware that in a dialogue session held in a university tonight (Oct 10), one female student claimed that after being arrested, she was sexually assaulted by Police officers when she was detained in the San Uk Ling Holding Centre.<br />\n<br />\nThe Police accord high priority to such a serious allegation. So far, the Complaints Against Police Office has not received any complaint of sexual assault related to the San Uk Ling Holding Centre. We will proactively contact the female and appeal to her to provide concrete evidence so that we can launch a fair fact-finding investigation as soon as possible."},{"pid":"045f98fdd55d1d58478efd91c761ac883b8ec5d0","tid":1644730,"uid":72381,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"好快又變成被告，誹謗<br />\n唔會有CCTV亦都無仇報<br />\n無人性嫁班狗"},{"pid":"743728884634afc5292fcf58e839220b39ca23d2","tid":1644730,"uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"原告成被告都唔驚<br />\n上面土共都癡線<br />\n可能強姦完 好似光頭sir咁<br />\n變撚埋英雄 個位強姦警員<br />\n送埋勛章+再加強姦獎金"},{"pid":"8925a2edcbda4fc33eff90cd228f4407c3feadbe","tid":1644730,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母你班警犬唔好諗住殺人滅口<br />\nYou will pay for it"},{"pid":"b3503c53aad2e71e7720778846897b4156909ac6","tid":1644730,"uid":274772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201